Package: medsim
Type: Package
Title: Simulation Infrastructure for Mediation Analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Date: 2025-12-03
Authors@R: person("Davood", "Tofighi",
    email = "dtofighi@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8523-7776"))
Maintainer: Davood Tofighi <dtofighi@gmail.com>
Description: Provides standardized infrastructure for conducting Monte Carlo
    simulation studies in mediation analysis. Features include environment-aware
    execution (local vs HPC cluster), parallel processing with progress reporting,
    ground truth caching, automated result analysis, and publication-ready
    visualization. Designed to work seamlessly with the mediation analysis
    ecosystem: 'medfit', 'probmed', 'RMediation', and 'medrobust'.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://github.com/data-wise/medsim,
    https://data-wise.github.io/medsim/
BugReports: https://github.com/data-wise/medsim/issues
